  "title": "Brand Ambassador (ENTRY - LEVEL / LEADERSHIP)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Not Your Usual 9–5—Adventure Awaits!</strong><br /><br /><strong>As we expand, we are looking out for motivated and self-driven individuals to join our marketing team! We work closely with local brands to help execute campaigns through face-to-face marketing.</strong></p><p><strong>If you are someone who enjoys talking with people, working in a vibrant and energetic company, this role may be for you!</strong><br /></p><p><strong>⚡Responsibilities:</strong><br /><br />- Promote products and services from clients<br />- Work with the sales and marketing team to achieve sales targets<br />- Ensure marketing campaigns are executed smoothly<br /><br />⚡<strong>Who we are looking for:</strong><br /><br />- Willing to learn new skills with an open mindset<br />- Career paths with built-in travel<br />- Can work well in team orientated environment<br /><br />⚡<strong>Career Perks:</strong></p><p>📈 Promotions based on performance, not seniority<br />📈 Training in brand building, sales strategy & team leadership<br />📈 Join a network of ambitious marketers and entrepreneurs<br /><br /><strong>Apply now to find out more!</strong></p><p><strong>Note: **Singaporean/PR Applicants Only!</strong></p><p><strong>Click APPLY NOW or contact 9145 2411 (WhatsApp)</strong><br /><br /><br /><strong>Shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</strong></p>",
